children.text: Spruce Bar is located inside of the upper level of Spruce Base Lodge
Spruce Camp food court is located on the upper level of Spruce Camp
Full service bar with hybrid style restaurant
Octagon is a quick service style restaurant
Located under the Mountain Gondola adjacent to the Midway parking lot

Cliff House is a hybrid style restaurant where you order at the bar and a server delivers your food to the table. Full bar is available and kids menu are available. The views are beautiful but gondola ride to access this mountain top restaurant is not included in the price of lunch.
